      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Nocturnal Nuisances",
        "Client": "Honest Night Watch Captain",
        "Description": "We\u0027ve been getting more and more\r\nreports of Anjanath and Tobi-Kadachi\r\nassaults in the Jungle as of late.\r\nGuarding the night roads is our job,\r\nbut their ferocity is overwhelming\r\nand many a guard has been injured.\r\nCould you do something about them?",
        "Target": "Hunt an Anjanath and a Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Nuisances nocturnes",
        "Client": "Capitaine de vigie de nuit",
        "Description": "Depuis quelque temps, il y a\r\nbeaucoup d\u0027attaques d\u0027Anjanath\r\net de Tobi-Kadachi dans la Jungle.\r\nNotre travail consiste \u00E0 garder\r\nles routes, la nuit, mais ces\r\nmonstres sont vraiment trop\r\nf\u00E9roces. Tu peux t\u0027en charger ?",
        "Target": "Chasser un Anjanath et un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Inconvenienti notturni",
        "Client": "Capitano di guardia onesto",
        "Description": "Di recente riceviamo sempre\r\npi\u00F9 segnalazioni di attacchi di\r\nAnjanath e Tobi-Kadachi nella\r\ngiungla. \u00C8 compito nostro\r\nproteggere le strade di notte,\r\nma la loro ferocia \u00E8 troppo\r\nper noi. Puoi sconfiggerli tu?",
        "Target": "Caccia un Anjanath e un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "St\u00F6renfriede in der Nacht",
        "Client": "Ehrlicher Nachtwachekapit\u00E4n",
        "Description": "Neuerdings erhalten wir mehr\r\nBerichte \u00FCber Anjanath- und Tobi-\r\nKadachi-Angriffe im Dschungel.\r\nDie n\u00E4chtlichen Stra\u00DFen zu\r\nbewachen ist unsere Aufgabe,\r\ndoch die Wildheit ist zu viel f\u00FCr\r\nuns. Kannst du sie besiegen?",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Anjanath und einen\r\nTobi-Kadachi.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Molestias nocturnas",
        "Client": "Capit\u00E1n nocturno honesto",
        "Description": "\u00DAltimamente cada vez hay m\u00E1s\r\nasaltos de Anjanath y Tobi-\r\nKadachi en la Jungla. Nosotros\r\nvigilamos el camino de noche,\r\npero tanta ferocidad nos\r\nsupera. \u00BFTendr\u00EDas la bondad\r\nde solucionar el problema?",
        "Target": "Caza un Anjanath\r\ny un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041D\u043E\u0447\u043D\u044B\u0435 \u043D\u0435\u043F\u0440\u0438\u044F\u0442\u043D\u043E\u0441\u0442\u0438",
